			img.fragment.height-330(src=imgAssets+'sp_prince_06.png')
+frameInbox('New mechanics are introduced once they\'re needed')
	ul
		li.fragment The game should introduce new mechanics/items at the moment of they need
		li.fragment New enemies should show up, once the player possesses the skill and equipment to defeat them
	figure.top-120.left-20.fragment
		img.height-320(src=imgAssets+'intro_gravitygun.jpg')
